IT Budget




Delphi Automotive plc is the European division of Delphi Holdings LLP, a global automotive parts company based in Troy, Michigan, United States. Delphi provides mechanical and car parts for manufacturers as well as aftermarket parts for consumer purchase.
Delphi Automotive plc is the European division of Delphi Holdings LLP, a global automotive parts company based in Troy, Michigan, United States. Delphi provides mechanical and car parts for manufacturers as well as aftermarket parts for consumer purchase.

IT Priorities
•SAP is Delphi's… MoreDelphi Automotive plc is the European division of Delphi Holdings LLP, a global automotive parts company based in Troy, Michigan, United States. Delphi provides mechanical and car parts for manufacturers as well as aftermarket parts for consumer purchase.

IT Priorities
•SAP is Delphi's primary enterprise resource planning (ERP) software platform.

IT Structure
•The executive leadership and most of the IT operations for Delphi are located at the company's American headquarters located in Troy, Michigan, United States.
•For more information on Delphi's American IT operations, please see the profile for Delphi Holdings LLP.
•Delphi Diesel Systems is a part of the Energy & Chassis Division of the Delphi Corporation.

IT Vendors
•Most of the company's data center operations are hosted with HP's data center services.
•CSC provides much of the company's applications support, including the implementation of SAP.

IT Intelligence Snippets

2013
•The company is currently consolidating the SharePoint layout in the area of metrics analysis.

2012
•SAP is Delphi's primary enterprise resource planning (ERP) software platform.
•Within the United Kingdom, there is a small team for systems administration to handle internal servers and networks with locations in the UK.
•Delphi also has teams for software programming, which operate on product-side and internal-side services.
•The company also uses SharePoint for collaboration, this is part of a global SharePoint environment maintained by headquarters.





