Delphi Home/ About











Print





 











Delphi Automotive PLC (NYSE: DLPH)
is a high-technology company that integrates safer, greener and more connected solutions for the automotive and transportation sectors. Headquartered in Gillingham, U.K., Delphi operates technical centers, manufacturing sites and customer support services in 46 countries.

At Delphi, we are driven by meaningful innovation. We see the future of driving and are making it possible today. We envision a society with zero road fatalities, zero injuries and zero accidents. 












